OL,6,FA mother-of-two operated on by
OL,7,Fdisgraced breast surgeon Ian Paterson
OL,8,Fwas not told that other medical
OL,9,Fexperts believed treatment he
OL,10,Frecommended was not the safest option,
OL,11,Fan inquest has heard.
OL,13,FThe third of 62 inquests being held on
OL,14,Fpatients of Paterson, who is serving a
OL,15,F20-year sentence for wounding, was
OL,16,Ftold Christine Baker died aged 59 in
OL,17,F2015, after putting her trust in his
OL,18,Fadvice to have a "skin-sparing"
OL,19,Fmastectomy in 2005.
OL,26,@zD@ROUzD@_O]
