OL,3,CMother-of-two operated on by disgraced
OL,4,Csurgeon not given 'safest' treatment
OL,6,FHer husband Stephen Baker told the
OL,7,Finquest on Monday that his wife, an
OL,8,FEnglish teacher at a Birmingham
OL,9,Fsecondary school, had been advised
OL,10,Fthat there was "no additional risk" to
OL,11,Fa reconstructive element of the
OL,12,Fprocedure, but saw her cancer "return"
OL,13,Fin 2007 and underwent a second
OL,14,Fmastectomy.
OL,26,@rD@POUrD@cO]tD@_OUtD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/14
