OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F372A1730770327
OL,3,CMother-of-two operated on by disgraced
OL,4,Csurgeon not given 'safest' treatment
OL,6,FAt the start of his evidence, Mr
OL,7,FBaker, a retired automotive design
OL,8,Fengineer from Balsall Common, near
OL,9,FSolihull, described Mrs Baker as
OL,10,Fsomeone who was passionate about
OL,11,Feducation and did her best to give her
OL,12,Fpupils the best chance in life.
OL,14,FPaterson, 66, told Birmingham
OL,15,FCoroner's Court last week that he
OL,16,Fstopped performing his version of the
OL,17,F"cleavage-sparing" operation as soon
OL,18,Fas he was informed by hospital chiefs
OL,19,Fin 2007 that more research was needed.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/14
