OL,3,CMother-of-two operated on by disgraced
OL,4,Csurgeon not given 'safest' treatment
OL,6,FHe told the inquest: "She wasn't
OL,7,Freally keen to have immediate
OL,8,Freconstruction.
OL,10,F"It was just that she had been advised
OL,11,Fthat that was the best option so she
OL,12,Fjust went along with it."
OL,14,FA nurse, who appeared to be a "big
OL,15,Fdevotee" of Paterson, also helped
OL,16,Fpersuade Mrs Baker to have the
OL,17,Freconstructive procedure, Mr Baker
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,26,@nD@VOUrD@AOUtD@YO]vD@_OUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/14
