OL,3,CMother-of-two operated on by disgraced
OL,4,Csurgeon not given 'safest' treatment
OL,6,FAnswering questions from counsel to
OL,7,Fthe inquests Jonathan Jones KC, Mr
OL,8,FBaker added: "We were pushed really
OL,9,Fdown the route of having a skin-
OL,10,Fsparing mastectomy with immediate
OL,11,Freconstruction and also we were
OL,12,Fpersuaded to use the private sector as
OL,13,Fwell.
OL,15,F"I think in hindsight now we would
OL,16,Fhave gone for a straightforward
OL,17,Fmastectomy without a reconstruction in
OL,18,Fthe private or NHS sector, whichever
OL,19,Fwas the fastest."
OL,26,@pD@NOUwD@AOU{D@QO]
