OL,6,FThe inquest heard pathology tests were
OL,7,Fconducted after the first mastectomy
OL,8,Ftook place in March 2005 and Mrs Baker
OL,9,Fwas told the operation had "gone well".
OL,11,FMr Baker said he only found out after
OL,12,Fa 2020 inquiry report into Paterson's
OL,13,Fmalpractice that it was suggested
OL,14,Ftissue had been "left behind" during
OL,15,Fthe operation.
OL,26,@qD@\OUqD@fO]vD@QOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/14
