OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F372A1730770327
OL,3,CMother-of-two operated on by disgraced
OL,4,Csurgeon not given 'safest' treatment
OL,6,FThe inquest heard a multi-disciplinary
OL,7,Fteam (MDT) discussed the course of
OL,8,Faction which should be taken, leaving
OL,9,Fthe couple puzzled.
OL,11,F"There was this exalted breast surgeon
OL,12,Fadvising us to take one course of
OL,13,Faction and the MDT suggesting that
OL,14,Fwasn't the right course of action," Mr
OL,15,FBaker said.
OL,17,FHe added: "I think people in the Trust
OL,18,Fwere starting to have concerns about
OL,19,FMr Paterson but we were totally
OL,20,Funaware of those concerns.
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@cO]yD@KOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
