CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F372A1730770327
OL,3,CMother-of-two operated on by disgraced
OL,4,Csurgeon not given 'safest' treatment
OL,6,F"So really we were being asked to make
OL,7,Fa decision without all the facts.
OL,9,F"We were still of the belief that Mr
OL,10,FPaterson was the best surgeon
OL,11,Favailable."
OL,13,FA letter presented to the inquest
OL,14,Fsuggested that members of the MDT
OL,15,Fbelieved delaying reconstruction until
OL,16,Fafter the second mastectomy was the
OL,17,Fsafest option, and Mr Paterson's
OL,18,Frecommendation had a "higher risk" of
OL,19,Flocal recurrence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUsD@KO]zD@VOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/14
