OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F372A1730770327
OL,3,CMother-of-two operated on by disgraced
OL,4,Csurgeon not given 'safest' treatment
OL,6,F"When Chris was diagnosed with breast
OL,7,Fcancer, she was so calm and had
OL,8,Falready started to think about the
OL,9,Fimplications on the journey home from
OL,10,Fhospital. Her main concern was how to
OL,11,Fbreak the news to our girls so that
OL,12,Fthey wouldn't be worried.
OL,14,F"People were amazed by Chris, she was
OL,15,Fso courageous, uncomplaining and
OL,16,Fstoical."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUxD@IO]
