OL,6,FPaterson, originally from Glasgow, who
OL,7,Fwas living in Altrincham in Greater
OL,8,FManchester when he was tried and
OL,9,Fconvicted, was employed by the Heart
OL,10,Fof England NHS Foundation Trust and
OL,11,Fpractised in the private sector at
OL,12,FSpire Parkway and Spire Little Aston.
OL,14,FHe was appointed as a consultant at
OL,15,FSolihull Hospital in 1998 and
OL,16,Fpractised there until May 2011.
OL,18,FThe inquest continues.
